<quote>
<url href="http://www.uwosh.edu/colleges/cols/rel_evol_sun.htm">Evolution Sunday</url> is part of a broader campaign begun a year ago called the <url href="http://www.uwosh.edu/colleges/cols/clergy_project.htm">Clergy Letter Project</url>. Through e-mail and word-of-mouth, 10,266 clergy have now signed an online letter backing evolution as "a foundational scientific truth, one that has stood up to rigorous scrutiny and upon which much of human knowledge and achievement rests."
</quote>

